But I did.

101
00:04:37.653 --> 00:04:39.923
I will fix this.

102
00:04:39.947 --> 00:04:42.384
Just stay out of it this time.

103
00:04:42.408 --> 00:04:44.076
I don't need your help.

104
00:04:47.204 --> 00:04:48.306
Good morning. students.

105
