120
00:05:32.624 --> 00:05:34.626
Okay. keep... just keep talking.

121
00:05:36.378 --> 00:05:40.716
To put it in a vernacular
I think you'll all understand...

122
00:05:41.717 --> 00:05:44.070
"What else should I be?

123
00:05:44.094 --> 00:05:46.680
All apologies."

124
00:05:47.890 --> 00:05:48.891
Kurt Cobain.

