769
00:38:31.059 --> 00:38:33.121
I know you.

770
00:38:33.145 --> 00:38:34.747
Your heart's still there.

771
00:38:34.771 --> 00:38:38.167
But I don't want
to make the same mistakes as last time.

772
00:38:38.191 --> 00:38:41.671
Our friendship means so much to me.

773
00:38:41.695 --> 00:38:44.048
and I want to be better
about checking in and visiting.

774
00:38:44.072 --> 00:38:46.718
You know. the thing about being friends

775
00:38:46.742 --> 00:38:48.970
with someone like you

776
00:38:48.994 --> 00:38:51.121
is knowing when to let them shine.

777
00:38:52.330 --> 00:38:54.875
-Mm.
-Mm.

778
00:39:01.214 --> 00:39:02.632
Here we go.

